headline: Evercore ISI Raises Fifth Third Bancorp (FITB) Price Target After Q4 Earnings Review
summary: Fifth Third Bancorp (NASDAQ:FITB) is included among 13 Best Long Term Low Risk Stocks to Buy Now. On February 5, Evercore ISI lifted its price target on Fifth Third Bancorp (NASDAQ:FITB) to $57 from $52 and kept an In Line rating.
